Personal Information that you provide

AMENDMENTS

You will be deemed to have agreed to the amended Terms by your continued use of the Platforms following the date on which the amended Terms are posted.

PAYMENT

StackFood reserves the right to offer additional payment methods and/or remove existing payment methods at any time in its sole discretion. If you choose to pay using an online payment method, the payment shall be processed by our third party payment service provider(s). With your consent, your credit card / payment information will be stored with our third party payment service provider(s) for future orders. Insofar as required, StackFood takes responsibility for payments made on our Platforms including refunds, chargebacks, cancellations and dispute resolution, provided if reasonable and justifiable and in accordance with these Terms.

CANCELLATION

This is a Demo Privacy Policy

This policy explains how StackFood website and related applications (the “Site”, “we” or “us”) collects, uses, shares and protects the personal information that we collect through this site or different channels. 🛒 1. General Refund Eligibility

 

You may be eligible for a refund in the following situations:

• You did not receive your order

• You received the wrong item(s)

• Your parcel delivery was not fulfilled as agreed

• A technical or billing error occurred during payment

🥗 2. Food & Grocery Orders

 

Due to the perishable nature of food items, returns are not accepted. However, you may be eligible for a refund or store credit if:

• Items arrived spoiled, damaged, or missing

• You were charged for items you did not receive

 

To request a refund, contact us within 24 hours of delivery with:

• Order number

• Photos (if applicable)

• Description of the issue

 

 

📦 3. E-Commerce Products

 

If you ordered a non-perishable product:

Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the return is due to a defect or error on our part.

🚚 5. Parcel & Courier Services

 

Refunds are available if:

Welcome to Tamam!

At Tamam, we believe in creating exceptional experiences that bring people together. Our passion for delivering high-quality products and services drives everything we do, and we are dedicated to ensuring that each of our customers and businesses feels valued and cared for. Whether you’re here for our platform, or to learn more about our mission, we are thrilled to have you as part of our journey.

Our Story

We came up with the idea of Tamam after a pistachio latte in an Erbil coffee shop. The founders were struck by the excitement and optimism of the coffee shop's owners as they had just had their soft opening. We spoke to more businesses in the areas and all of them said the same thing; that they were paying expensive commissions and finding it difficult to control and grow their own business. 

Tamam was founded on the belief that all businesses should be able to grow. We started with a simple idea: to offer businesses the tools that not only meets the needs of our customers but exceeds their expectations. Since 2025, we’ve grown from a small operation to a thriving community of satisfied customers, thanks to our commitment to excellence and a team of dedicated professionals who are passionate about what they do.

Our Mission

Our mission at Tamam is to empower businesses and allow them to grow fairly and sustanianably. We strive to create innovative, sustainable, and reliable solutions that make a real difference in the lives of our customers. We’re committed to providing outstanding customer service, offering products/services that are both functional and stylish, and fostering an environment of trust and collaboration.

Why Choose Us?

  • Quality First: We take great pride in ensuring that every product/service we offer is of the highest quality.
  • Customer-Centric: Your satisfaction is our top priority. We’re here to support you at every step.
  • Innovation: We are constantly evolving and looking for ways to improve and offer the latest and best solutions to our customers.
  • Community: We believe in building strong relationships with our customers and our community, creating a positive impact wherever we go.

 

Our Team

Tamam is made up of passionate and experienced professionals who share a common goal: to provide outstanding products and services that make a difference. We work closely together to ensure that every project we undertake is completed with excellence, attention to detail, and integrity.

Thank you for choosing Tamam. We’re excited to be a part of your journey and look forward to serving you.

Get in Touch

Have any questions or want to learn more? Feel free to reach out to our friendly customer service team, and we’ll be happy to assist you.
